snippet.title: 《肥牛》晴天林｜荃灣火鍋放題貪心男女 生蠔肥牛蝦蟹乜都塞落袋（原曲：阿牛 - 陳奕迅）
snippet.description:
#火鍋放題 #肥牛 #陳奕迅

《肥牛》
原曲：阿牛 - 陳奕迅
改詞：梁栢堅 & 晴天林

一盤肥牛
職員嚟 即場拿出盤肥牛
可恨在 用隻手gel 埋油頭
經理看到咁大袋  才和我開口

埋單之前一刻才趕到
唔通有人通報才知道
這日任叫火鍋 叫咁大煲
怎能預計似這般  全入鏡全城望到
我哋打緊邊爐
開心到 當作入嚟尋寶

不甘心
尤其這紛爭   就像偷三牲
想過攞膠箱   我差點講真

成包生蝦早已將密實嘅袋去焗暈
再叫 十幾斤
份量足夠食飽四十人
約定日後 菜用嚟炆海蔘
拿來烚我尚有餘的冬粉
狂叫 再落海鮮七份
新鮮到 我再袋埋唐芹

好開心 袋住好開心
肥牛海鮮羹 返去滾一滾
不打緊
誰人不貪心 就是很貪心
拎了兩三斤  隻生蝦郁緊

執到寶
成包出前一丁拿得到
難得放題 拎晒來醫肚
往後自製生蝦蟹柳食譜
本來仲有更多的豬牛羊魚肉未到
最後拎啲生蠔
貪心到 叫我食神肥佬

很開心 袋住很開心
贈姨媽姑嬸 返去滾一滾
不打緊
誰人不貪心 就是很貪心
拎了兩三斤 又慳幾千蚊

一頭肥牛
走全場 收埋甜蝦和肥牛
慘淡在侍應影低我眉頭
一放上網即出名 點樣走
我食牛 我食牛

snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV – "Back to War" In-Engine Trailer | PC Gaming Show Tokyo Direct
snippet.description:
Here’s your official look into the next evolution of the iconic real-time strategy franchise with Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV!
First revealed during PC Gaming Show: Tokyo Direct, this new trailer has been captured entirely from in-engine gameplay. 

Many years after the events of Dawn of War: Dark Crusade, Kronus burns as Space Marines of the Blood Ravens Chapter and their Adeptus Mechanicus allies clash with brutal Ork hordes. With victory almost certain, a new threat emerges: the Necrons. As this new faction overwhelms the battlefield, the Imperium must rebuild and grow their forces if they hope to stand a chance. 

Whether you’re a long-time fan of the series or brand new to the world of Dawn of War, this new trailer, captured entirely in-engine, provides a more detailed look at what to expect with exciting gameplay, action-packed cinematics, and a taste of the war-torn future that awaits.

At last, back to war! 
---

Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV releases on Steam in 2026!

snippet.title: Kaiju Cleanup - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Relax and unwind by cleaning up the world’s biggest corpses. Here's your look at Kaiju Cleanup announcement trailer for the upcoming cleaning simulation game. Kaiju Cleanup will be available on PC.

When colossal alien titans run rampant until getting domed by a railgun, the world finds itself in need of a true hero. That’s you: a Kaiju Cleaner who won’t be perturbed by petty concerns like “workplace injury” or “life expectancy”. After another Kaiju attack on the city, use your tools to clean up vast piles of dead monster until the zone is safe for reconstruction. The Kaiju may be dead, but its corpse is leaking radiation, seeping acidic fluids, concealing explosive organs, and generally making the area inhospitable to any other form of life. You’ll probably die as you go about your work, but that’s fine; send another clone, mop up your corpse, and carry on.

Baapu ghrey betha hlle shonk poorda ni
Jaffa mitraa da kotli aaley de wangu 
Bhjjda begana bnda kde bahli door na ni 

5-7 lakh guddiyan te laa dyiye
Jehdi chldi nhi jaan ohchay paa dyiye
Akhh chandri eda di tere yaar di ni
Urrhdi hoyi sheh nu koley farh k betha lyiye 
Maa da putt na kde v kalla gheriye
Chaar bndey lai k maadey te na vehriye
Koley asley da maan v koi na plle 
Jigraa bdaa aa billo mukki rooh na feriye 

Kalli vass ch kridi ohi cheez jehdi 
Athri aa duniya draa k rkhdi ,
Gaddi chli aa kabaddia nu yaar di te 
Vapsi te aundi kudey cup chkdi 
Ena tagrah ae mitraa da bol ni
Billo dalley nal dinda dalla jorh ni 
Kuttey billeyan di hva nhi koi v 
Sandd shuru to bde c taaya chacheyan de kol ni 
Zumevaari eni kehli te pugaliye
Paisa dhela hun suttey pye kma lyiye

Check kri height saadiya udaarian di

snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
snippet.description:
New game drops! Developers! More!

Minecraft LIVE is our own super special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! 

We’re updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more! 

After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

snippet.title: MIBR vs. NRG — VALORANT Champions Paris — Playoffs Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world’s top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We’re proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:
Twitter/X: @valorantesports
Facebook: /valorantesports
Instagram: @valorantesports
TikTok: @valorantesports
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/valorant
